accordions.message:
We may collect the following personal information when you use our services:

a) Contact information such as full name, email address, and phone number;
b) Profile information such as profile picture, date of birth, gender, location, and other profile information you choose to share;
c) Information about your activity on our social network, including your posts, comments, and interactions with other users;
d) Information about the device you use to access our services, such as device model, operating system, and IP address.

We use your personal information to provide and improve our services, including:

a) Personalizing your experience on our platform;
b) Providing customer support services;
c) Sending relevant communications, such as service updates and promotions;
d) Conducting data analysis to improve our services and understand our users' needs.

We do not share your personal information with third parties except in the following circumstances:
a) When we are required by law to disclose your information;
b) When we believe that disclosure is necessary to protect our legal rights or those of third parties;
c) When we provide information to service providers who help us provide our services.

You are responsible for the proper use of our platform and must comply with all applicable laws and regulations. By using our services, you agree not to:

a) Post illegal, defamatory, offensive, obscene, threatening, or abusive content;
b) Engage in fraudulent activities, such as phishing or identity fraud;
c) Commit acts that may harm the platform or other users, such as using malware or spam;
d) Infringe on the intellectual property rights of third parties;
e) Access or attempt to access the platform by any means other than through the interfaces provided by our social network.
